"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Donald Trump said that after the Iranian ship ignored warnings, the US navy damaged its engine room. The US has shared video of this attack.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Navy Damages Iranian Ship\",            \"translated_version\": \"Donald Trump dijo que despu\u00e9s de que el barco iran\u00ed ignor\u00f3 las advertencias, la marina de EE.UU. da\u00f1\u00f3 su sala de motores. EE.UU. comparti\u00f3 un video de este ataque.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Marina de EE.UU. da\u00f1a barco iran\u00ed\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Japan's weather agency warns that a stronger earthquake might happen in the next week.\",            \"english_title\": \"Japan Earthquake Warning\",            \"translated_version\": \"La agencia de clima de Jap\u00f3n advierte que un terremoto m\u00e1s fuerte podr\u00eda ocurrir la pr\u00f3xima semana.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Advertencia de terremoto en Jap\u00f3n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Businesses can apply online for refunds that are expected to total $160 billion.\",            \"english_title\": \"Businesses Can Apply for Refunds\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las empresas pueden solicitar reembolsos en l\u00ednea que se espera que sumen $160 mil millones.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Empresas pueden pedir reembolsos\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Israeli military is very concerned about a soldier's actions, and the US ambassador wants quick consequences.\",            \"english_title\": \"Concerns Over Soldier's Actions\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ej\u00e9rcito israel\u00ed est\u00e1 muy preocupado por las acciones de un soldado, y el embajador de EE.UU. quiere consecuencias r\u00e1pidas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Preocupaci\u00f3n por acciones de soldado\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Three boys and five girls, aged between three to 11, were killed in a shooting on Sunday, according to officials.\",            \"english_title\": \"Children Killed in Shooting\",            \"translated_version\": \"Tres ni\u00f1os y cinco ni\u00f1as, de entre tres y once a\u00f1os, murieron en un tiroteo el domingo, seg\u00fan funcionarios.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ni\u00f1os muertos en tiroteo\"        }    ]}"